Description: Microscope measurement tool using OpenCV
 Microscopi is a Linux desktop tool for real-time calibrated
 measurements using a USB microscope or camera.
 Supports distance, radius, square and coordinate measurements,
 calibration, export to PNG/CSV and PCB workflows.
